description: Gyro George, a thriving family business, is such a beloved Northeast Ohio staple, there are 10 brick and mortar locations serving the locals delicious breakfast, wraps, and sandwiches each day. Now you can enjoy their famously mouthwatering menu on the streets, courtesy of the Gyro George truck.  With its scrumptious selection of big breakfast combos with fried eggs, pancakes, sausages, etc... as well as warm gyros, fresh hot hand-cut fries, and so much more, it’s no wonder Gyro George was rated as Cleveland’s favorite food truck on scoutology.com. If you wish to gorge on some great tasting grub, come on out to Gyro George!
name: Gyro George
